---
title: Italian Beef Ragu & Rosemary Pangrattato with Fettuccine & Pear Salad
description: This sumptuous yet simple pasta is absolute decadence, from the rich beef ragu infused with Italian herbs, to the bite from the grated Parmesan cheese. Don’t be too surprised if the bowls are left licked clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-beef-ragu-rosemary-pangrattato-ed2fba8c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/italian-beef-ragu-rosemary-pangrattato-5f7e61005e14b77162179c93-bdb6f49b.pdf
